Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:windowtext\">detailed budget table/calculator</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-US\"> </span><i><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:&#10;EN-IE;mso-fareast-language:FR-BE\">(template available in the Submission System)</span></i><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Arial;color:windowtext;mso-fareast-language:EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;&#10;margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:windowtext;mso-fareast-language:EN-US\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-US\">list of previous projects (key projects for the last 4 years)</span><i><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:&#10;EN-IE;mso-fareast-language:FR-BE\"> </span></i><i><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE\">(template available in Part B</span></i><i><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;mso-fareast-language:FR-BE\">)</span></i><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Arial;color:windowtext;mso-fareast-language:EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:&#10;10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:&#10;10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:windowtext;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">Please note that the amounts entered into the summarised budget table (filled in directly online) must correspond to the amounts calculated in the detailed budget table.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Text1\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;tab-stops:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Your application must be <b>readable</b></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">, </span><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\">accessible and</span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\">printable</span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\">.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"Text1\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;tab-stops:36.0pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proposal page limits and layout:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;described in Part B of the Application Form available in the Submission System and as below:</span></p>\r\n<p>Proposals are limited to maximum&nbsp;<b>70 pages&nbsp;</b>(Part B). Evaluators will not consider any additional pages. Shorter proposals are welcome.</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2. Eligible countries:&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in section 6 of of the call document and as below:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"Text1\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;&#10;margin-left:0cm;tab-stops:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Arial\">In order to be eligible, the applicants (beneficiaries and affiliated entities) must:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;&#10;margin-left:35.45pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-pagination:none;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Arial\">be established in one of the eligible countries, i.e.:</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\">EU Member States (including overseas countries and territories (OCTs)).</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. Other eligibility conditions:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;described&nbsp;</span>as below and in more detail in section 6 of the call document :</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"Text1\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;&#10;margin-left:0cm;tab-stops:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Arial\">In order to be eligible, the applicants (beneficiaries and affiliated entities) must:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;&#10;margin-left:35.45pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-pagination:none;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Arial\">be legal entities (public or private bodies)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;&#10;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:35.45pt;text-align:left;text-indent:-17.85pt;&#10;mso-pagination:none;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">be an organisation active in the field of sport (such as a sport federation or club), with legal personality (public or private body).</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Beneficiaries and affiliated entities must register in the </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/how-to-participate/participant-register\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Participant Register</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">&mdash; </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">before submitting the proposal </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri\">&mdash; and will have to </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">be validated by the Central Validation Service (REA Validation). For the validation, they will be requested to upload documents showing legal status and origin.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">Other entities may participate in other consortium roles, such as associated partners, subcontractors, third parties giving in-kind contributions, etc </span><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">(see section 13)</span></i><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>4. Financial and operational capacity and exclusion:&nbsp;</b>summarised below. For a detailed description, consult&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">section 7 of the call document:</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Verdana;color:black;mso-fareast-language:&#10;EN-GB\">Applicants must have <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">stable and sufficient resources</b> to </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">successfully implement the projects and contribute their share. Organisations participating in several projects must have sufficient capacity to implement all these projects.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Verdana;color:black;mso-fareast-language:&#10;EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Text3\" style=\"margin-left:0cm\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:&#10;italic\">Applicants must have the <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">know-how, qualifications</b></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">and</span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:&#10;italic\">resources</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:&#10;italic\">to successfully implement the projects and contribute their share (including sufficient experience in projects of comparable size and nature).<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"FR-BE\">5.&nbsp;Evaluation and award procedure:&nbsp;</span></b>described in section 8 of the call document</p>\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Award criteria, scoring and thresholds:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;described in section 9 of the call document</span></li>\r\n</ul>\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">Submission and&nbsp; process</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>described&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">section 11 of the call document&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n    <li><span lang=\"EN-US\">Evaluation process: described&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">section 8 of the call document and the</span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/om_en.pdf\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Online Manual</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Indicative timeline for evaluation and grant agreement:&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in section 4 of the call document and in the table below:</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTa